title: Millionaire Makers: 2 Stocks That Could've Made You Rich From a $10,000 Investment
description: None of America's greatest companies were built in a day, and in many cases, it has been worthwhile waiting a decade (or more) for the payoff.  Investors in the initial public offerings (IPOs) of Tesla (NASDAQ: TSLA) and Netflix (NASDAQ: NFLX) can attest to that.  Tesla might be one of the most diverse bets in the technology sector.
